01-17-15 9:25 am	SELECT
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id

01-17-15 10:51 am	SELECT
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id

01-17-15 11:25 am	SELECT
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id

01-17-15 11:33 am	SELECT
                  p.id,
                  p.first_name,
                  p.last_name,
                  p.description,
                  p.adult,
                  p.active,
                  DATE_FORMAT(a.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') attendance_dt,
                  a.first,
                  a.second
                FROM
                  People p
                  LEFT OUTER JOIN Attendance a ON p.id=a.attended_by

                  p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
                  p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,

01-17-15 11:36 am	SELECT
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description

		  People p

		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-19-15 2:17 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type =3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		  GROUP BY 
		    p.idvisited =  'false'

01-19-15 2:24 pm	SELECT
                    p.id,
                    CASE WHEN p.adult = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END adult,
                    p.first_name,
                    p.last_name,
                    p.description,
                    COUNT(1) Total_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.first) First_Service_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.second) Second_Service_Attendance
                  FROM
                    People p
                    INNER JOIN Attendance a ON a.attended_by=p.id
                  WHERE
                    (a.first = 1
                      OR a.second = 1)
                    AND (a.attendance_dt >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
                        AND a.attendance_dt <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y'))
                    AND p.active=1
                  GROUP BY
                    p.id
                  ORDER BY
                    Total_Attendance DESC,
                    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
                    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
                    p.last_name,
                    p.first_name,
                    p.description
01-19-15 2:24 pm	:fromDate => 01/01/2015
01-19-15 2:24 pm	:toDate => 01/19/2015
01-19-15 2:24 pm	Success

01-19-15 2:26 pm	:user_id => 1
01-19-15 2:26 pm	:session_id => 54bd545da7b0d2.09488485
01-19-15 2:26 pm	Success: TRUE
01-19-15 2:26 pm	1
01-19-15 2:26 pm	SELECT
                    p.id,
                    CASE WHEN p.adult = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END adult,
                    p.first_name,
                    p.last_name,
                    p.description,
                    COUNT(1) Total_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.first) First_Service_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.second) Second_Service_Attendance
                  FROM
                    People p
                    INNER JOIN Attendance a ON a.attended_by=p.id
                  WHERE
                    (a.first = 1
                      OR a.second = 1)
                    AND (a.attendance_dt >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
                        AND a.attendance_dt <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y'))
                    AND p.active=1
                  GROUP BY
                    p.id
                  ORDER BY
                    Total_Attendance DESC,
                    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
                    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
                    p.last_name,
                    p.first_name,
                    p.description

		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND p.commitment_baptism = 1
		    AND p.baptized = 0

		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND f.follow_up_date >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')

01-19-15 3:02 pm	SELECT
		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id

		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND f.follow_up_date >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND f.follow_up_date <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')

01-19-15 3:05 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1

		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-19-15 3:06 pm	SELECT
		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-19-15 3:07 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND f.follow_up_date >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND f.follow_up_date <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')

01-19-15 3:32 pm	SELECT
                    p.id,
                    CASE WHEN p.adult = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END adult,
                    p.first_name,
                    p.last_name,
                    p.description,
                    COUNT(1) Total_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.first) First_Service_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.second) Second_Service_Attendance
                  FROM
                    People p
                    INNER JOIN Attendance a ON a.attended_by=p.id
                  WHERE
                    (a.first = 1
                      OR a.second = 1)
		    AND p.active=1
		    AND f.follow_up_date >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND f.follow_up_date <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
                  GROUP BY
                    p.id
                  ORDER BY
                    Total_Attendance DESC,
                    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
                    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
                    p.last_name,
                    p.first_name,
                    p.description

                    CASE WHEN p.adult = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END adult,
                    p.first_name,
                    p.last_name,
                    p.description,
                    COUNT(1) Total_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.first) First_Service_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.second) Second_Service_Attendance
                  FROM
                    People p
                    INNER JOIN Attendance a ON a.attended_by=p.id
                  WHERE
                    (a.first = 1
                      OR a.second = 1)
		    AND p.active=1
		    AND f.follow_up_date >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND f.follow_up_date <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
                  GROUP BY
                    p.id
                  ORDER BY
                    Total_Attendance DESC,
                    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
                    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
                    p.last_name,
                    p.first_name,
                    p.description

                    p.id,
                    CASE WHEN p.adult = 1 THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END adult,
                    p.first_name,
                    p.last_name,
                    p.description,
                    COUNT(1) Total_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.first) First_Service_Attendance,

                  FROM
                    People p
                    INNER JOIN Attendance a ON a.attended_by=p.id
                  WHERE

                      OR a.second = 1)
                    AND (a.attendance_dt >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
                        AND a.attendance_dt <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y'))
                    AND p.active=1
                  GROUP BY
                    p.id

                    Total_Attendance DESC,

01-19-15 3:47 pm	SELECT
                    COUNT(1) Total_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.first) First_Service_Attendance,
                    SUM(a.second) Second_Service_Attendance,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=1 AND a.first=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=1 AND a.second=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=0 AND a.first=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=0 AND a.second=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) Second_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    DATE_FORMAT(attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') Attendance_dt
                  FROM
                    People p
                    INNER JOIN Attendance a ON a.attended_by=p.id
                  WHERE
                    (a.first = 1
                      OR a.second = 1)
		    AND p.active=1
		    AND a.attendance_dt >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND a.attendance_dt <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
                  GROUP BY
                    a.attendance_dt
                  ORDER BY
                    a.attendance_dt DESC

01-19-15 3:47 pm	SELECT
                    AVG(totals.Total_Attendance) Avg_Total_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.First_Service_Attendance) Avg_First_Service_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.Second_Service_Attendance) Avg_Second_Service_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.First_Service_Adult_Attendance) Avg_First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.Second_Service_Adult_Attendance) Avg_Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.First_Service_Kid_Attendance) Avg_First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.Second_Service_Kid_Attendance) Avg_Second_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.Total_Attendance) Max_Total_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.First_Service_Attendance) Max_First_Service_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.Second_Service_Attendance) Max_Second_Service_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.First_Service_Adult_Attendance) Max_First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.Second_Service_Adult_Attendance) Max_Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.First_Service_Kid_Attendance) Max_First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.Second_Service_Kid_Attendance) Max_Second_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.Total_Attendance) Min_Total_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.First_Service_Attendance) Min_First_Service_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.Second_Service_Attendance) Min_Second_Service_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.First_Service_Adult_Attendance) Min_First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.Second_Service_Adult_Attendance) Min_Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.First_Service_Kid_Attendance) Min_First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.Second_Service_Kid_Attendance) Min_Second_Service_Kid_Attendance
                  FROM (
                    SELECT
                      COUNT(1) Total_Attendance,
                      SUM(a.first) First_Service_Attendance,
                      SUM(a.second) Second_Service_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=1 AND a.first=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=1 AND a.second=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=0 AND a.first=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=0 AND a.second=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) Second_Service_Kid_Attendance
                    FROM
                      People p
                      INNER JOIN Attendance a ON a.attended_by=p.id
                    WHERE
                    (a.first = 1
                      OR a.second = 1)
		    AND p.active=1
		    AND a.attendance_dt >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND a.attendance_dt <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
                    GROUP BY
                      a.attendance_dt
                  ) totals

                    AVG(totals.Second_Service_Attendance) Avg_Second_Service_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.First_Service_Adult_Attendance) Avg_First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.Second_Service_Adult_Attendance) Avg_Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.First_Service_Kid_Attendance) Avg_First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    AVG(totals.Second_Service_Kid_Attendance) Avg_Second_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.Total_Attendance) Max_Total_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.First_Service_Attendance) Max_First_Service_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.Second_Service_Attendance) Max_Second_Service_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.First_Service_Adult_Attendance) Max_First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.Second_Service_Adult_Attendance) Max_Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.First_Service_Kid_Attendance) Max_First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    MAX(totals.Second_Service_Kid_Attendance) Max_Second_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.Total_Attendance) Min_Total_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.First_Service_Attendance) Min_First_Service_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.Second_Service_Attendance) Min_Second_Service_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.First_Service_Adult_Attendance) Min_First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.Second_Service_Adult_Attendance) Min_Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.First_Service_Kid_Attendance) Min_First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                    MIN(totals.Second_Service_Kid_Attendance) Min_Second_Service_Kid_Attendance
                  FROM (
                    SELECT
                      COUNT(1) Total_Attendance,
                      SUM(a.first) First_Service_Attendance,
                      SUM(a.second) Second_Service_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=1 AND a.first=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=1 AND a.second=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=0 AND a.first=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=0 AND a.second=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) Second_Service_Kid_Attendance
                    FROM
                      People p
                      INNER JOIN Attendance a ON a.attended_by=p.id
                    WHERE
                    (a.first = 1
                      OR a.second = 1)
		    AND p.active=1
		    AND a.attendance_dt >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
                    GROUP BY
                      a.attendance_dt
                  ) totals

                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=1 AND a.first=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) First_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=1 AND a.second=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) Second_Service_Adult_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=0 AND a.first=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) First_Service_Kid_Attendance,
                      SUM(CASE WHEN p.adult=0 AND a.second=1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) Second_Service_Kid_Attendance
                    FROM
                      People p
                      INNER JOIN Attendance a ON a.attended_by=p.id
                    WHERE
                    (a.first = 1
                      OR a.second = 1)
		    AND p.active=1
		    AND a.attendance_dt >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
                    GROUP BY
                      a.attendance_dt
                  ) totals

		  f.comments follow_up_comments,

		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		  GROUP BY 
		    p.id 
		  HAVING 
		    visited =  'false'

01-19-15 5:21 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND f.follow_up_date >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND f.follow_up_date <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		  GROUP BY 
		    p.id 
		  HAVING 
		    visited =  'false'

		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-19-15 5:40 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND f.follow_up_date >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND f.follow_up_date <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')

01-19-15 5:42 pm	SELECT
		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-19-15 6:01 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1

01-19-15 6:18 pm	SELECT
		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-19-15 6:20 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND p.info_gkids = 1

01-19-15 7:17 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND f.follow_up_date >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND f.follow_up_date <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')

01-19-15 8:21 pm	SELECT
		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.assigned_agent,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-19-15 9:45 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    p.primary_phone,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND p.assigned_agent = 0

                  p.id,
                  p.first_name,
                  p.last_name,
                  p.description,
                  p.adult,
                  p.active,
                  DATE_FORMAT(a.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') attendance_dt,
                  a.first,
                  a.second
                FROM
                  People p
                  LEFT OUTER JOIN Attendance a ON p.id=a.attended_by
                ORDER BY
                  p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
                  p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
                  p.last_name,
                  p.first_name,
                  p.description,
                  attendance_dt DESC

01-20-15 7:53 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    p.primary_phone,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.active = 1
		    AND f.follow_up_date >= STR_TO_DATE(:fromDate,'%m/%d/%Y')
		    AND f.follow_up_date <= STR_TO_DATE(:toDate,'%m/%d/%Y')

                  p.last_name,
                  p.description,

                  a.second

                  p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
                  p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
                  p.last_name,
                  p.first_name,
                  p.description,
                  attendance_dt DESC

		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.assigned_agent,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  FollowUps f
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.last_modified_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(),'%m/%d/%Y')
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.assigned_agent,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-20-15 10:07 pm	SELECT
		  f.follow_up_to_person_id person_id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id visitor_person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  FollowUps f
		  inner join People p on p.id=f.follow_up_to_person_id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.last_modified_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(),'%m/%d/%Y')
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.assigned_agent,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-21-15 6:16 pm	SELECT
		  f.follow_up_to_person_id person_id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id visitor_person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  FollowUps f
		  inner join People p on p.id=f.follow_up_to_person_id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.last_modified_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(),'%m/%d/%Y')
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		FROM

		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id

01-21-15 7:17 pm	SELECT
		  f.follow_up_to_person_id person_id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id visitor_person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  FollowUps f
		  inner join People p on p.id=f.follow_up_to_person_id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.last_modified_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(),'%m/%d/%Y')
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  p.id,

		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.assigned_agent,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  f.follow_up_to_person_id person_id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,

		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,

		  fp.description follow_up_description

		WHERE

		ORDER BY

		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  f.follow_up_to_person_id person_id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id visitor_person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  FollowUps f
		  inner join People p on p.id=f.follow_up_to_person_id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.last_modified_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(),'%m/%d/%Y')
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name,

		  FROM

		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id

                  DATE_FORMAT(a.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') attendance_dt,
                  a.first,
                  a.second
                FROM
                  People p
                  LEFT OUTER JOIN Attendance a ON p.id=a.attended_by
                ORDER BY
                  p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
                  p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
                  p.last_name,
                  p.first_name,
                  p.description,
                  attendance_dt DESC

		  f.follow_up_to_person_id person_id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id visitor_person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  FollowUps f
		  inner join People p on p.id=f.follow_up_to_person_id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.last_modified_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(),'%m/%d/%Y')
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-21-15 10:47 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    p.primary_phone,
		    p.street1,
		    p.street2,
		    p.city,
		    p.state,
		    p.zip,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.adult = 1
		    AND p.active = 1
		    AND p.info_visit = 1
		  ORDER BY
		    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.last_name,
		    p.first_name,
		    p.description

		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description

		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,

		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id

		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-21-15 10:56 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    p.primary_phone,
		    p.street1,
		    p.street2,
		    p.city,
		    p.state,
		    p.zip,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.adult = 1
		    AND p.active = 1
		  ORDER BY
		    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.last_name,
		    p.first_name,
		    p.description

01-22-15 5:41 pm	SELECT
		  f.follow_up_to_person_id person_id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id visitor_person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  FollowUps f
		  inner join People p on p.id=f.follow_up_to_person_id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.last_modified_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(),'%m/%d/%Y')
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-22-15 6:08 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    p.primary_phone,
		    p.street1,
		    p.street2,
		    p.city,
		    p.state,
		    p.zip,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.adult = 1
		    AND p.active = 1
		  ORDER BY
		    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.last_name,
		    p.first_name,
		    p.description

01-22-15 9:48 pm	:user_id => 1
01-22-15 9:48 pm	:session_id => 54c1b393570042.76341143
01-22-15 9:48 pm	Success: TRUE
01-22-15 9:48 pm	1
01-22-15 9:48 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    p.primary_phone,
		    p.street1,
		    p.street2,
		    p.city,
		    p.state,
		    p.zip,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.adult = 1
		    AND p.active = 1
		  ORDER BY
		    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.last_name,
		    p.first_name,
		    p.description

		    p.state,
		    p.zip,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.adult = 1
		    AND p.active = 1
		  ORDER BY
		    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.last_name,
		    p.first_name,
		    p.description

		  ORDER BY

01-22-15 10:30 pm	:user_id => 1
01-22-15 10:30 pm	:session_id => 54c1b393570042.76341143
01-22-15 10:30 pm	Success: TRUE
01-22-15 10:30 pm	1
01-22-15 10:30 pm	SELECT 
		    CASE WHEN vc.visit_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END visited, 
		    CASE WHEN tyc.ty_card_sent_count >0 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END ty_card_sent, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') communication_card_date, 
		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    p.primary_phone,
		    p.street1,
		    p.street2,
		    p.city,
		    p.state,
		    p.zip,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.adult = 1
		    AND p.active = 1
		  ORDER BY
		    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.last_name,
		    p.first_name,
		    p.description

01-22-15 10:47 pm	SELECT
		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.assigned_agent,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-23-15 5:19 pm	SELECT
		  f.follow_up_to_person_id person_id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id visitor_person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  FollowUps f
		  inner join People p on p.id=f.follow_up_to_person_id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.last_modified_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(),'%m/%d/%Y')
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-26-15 6:37 pm	SELECT
		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.assigned_agent,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-26-15 6:54 pm	SELECT
		  f.follow_up_to_person_id person_id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id visitor_person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  FollowUps f
		  inner join People p on p.id=f.follow_up_to_person_id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.last_modified_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(),'%m/%d/%Y')
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

01-26-15 7:36 pm	SELECT
		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.assigned_agent,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		    DATE_FORMAT(tyc.follow_up_date, '%m/%d/%Y') ty_card_date, 
		    p.id, 
		    p.first_name, 
		    p.last_name, 
		    p.description,
		    p.primary_phone,
		    p.street1,
		    p.street2,
		    p.city,
		    p.state,
		    p.zip,
		    CASE WHEN p.commitment_baptism = 1 THEN  'true' ELSE  'false' END commitment_baptism
		  FROM 
		    People p
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN FollowUps f ON f.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id AND f.type = 3
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) visit_count, follow_up_to_person_id FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =2)vc ON vc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		    LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT COUNT(*) ty_card_sent_count, follow_up_to_person_id, follow_up_date FROM FollowUps WHERE TYPE =5)tyc ON tyc.follow_up_to_person_id = p.id
		  WHERE 
		    p.adult = 1
		    AND p.active = 1
		    AND p.info_visit = 1
		  ORDER BY
		    p.last_name IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.description IS NOT NULL DESC,
		    p.last_name,
		    p.first_name,
		    p.description

		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM

01-29-15 9:37 pm	SELECT
		  DATE_FORMAT(at.attendance_dt,'%m/%d/%Y') first_attendance_dt,
		  p.id,
		  p.first_name,
		  p.last_name,
		  p.description,
		  DATE_FORMAT(p.first_visit,'%m/%d/%Y') first_visit,
		  p.active,
		  p.adult,
		  p.saved,
		  p.baptized,
		  p.member,
		  p.visitor,
		  p.assigned_agent,
		  p.street1,
		  p.street2,
		  p.city,
		  p.state,
		  p.zip,
		  p.email,
		  p.primary_phone,
		  p.secondary_phone,
		  p.commitment_christ,
		  p.recommitment_christ,
		  p.commitment_tithe,
		  p.commitment_ministry,
		  p.commitment_baptism,
		  p.info_next,
		  p.info_gkids,
		  p.info_ggroups,
		  p.info_gteams,
		  p.info_member,
		  p.info_visit,
		  f.id follow_up_id,
		  f.type follow_up_type,
		  DATE_FORMAT(f.follow_up_date,'%m/%d/%Y') follow_up_date,
		  f.comments follow_up_comments,
		  v.follow_up_id visitor_follow_up_id,
		  v.person_id,
		  fp.first_name follow_up_first_name,
		  fp.last_name follow_up_last_name,
		  fp.description follow_up_description
		FROM
		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
        GROUP BY
          p.id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date

		  (select min(attendance_dt) attendance_dt from Attendance a where a.attended_by=:id) at,
		  People p
		  left outer join FollowUps f on f.follow_up_to_person_id=p.id
		  left outer join FollowUpVisitors v on f.id=v.follow_up_id
		  left outer join People fp on fp.id=v.person_id
		WHERE
		  p.id=:id
        GROUP BY
          p.id
		ORDER BY
		  f.follow_up_date
